request.description:
Discounts are frequently provided to the guests. They can be transfer in the following ways according to the customer's reporting needs probably you can let the user to chose which one to use:

- **Transfer the discounted prices of the items** - No discount charge is required;
- **Transfer the total discount value with revenue category 'discount'** - One charge per bill per VAT group are needed;
- **Transfer the discounts separately for every item group / revenue category** - Separate charge for each item group / revenue category and VAT group is needed;

