*Update the housekeeping status for a room*

The list of statuses:

*   **""** (empty) - The room is clean and ready;
*   **"inspect"** - The room should be inspected;
*   **"progress"** - Cleaning in progress;
*   **"checked_out"** - The room haven't been cleaned after the check-out of the guest and will appear as **Dirty**. The Checked Out status is set automatically on the Booking Checkout

