request.description:
When you successfully tested all features covered by the integration with in-house tests we can move on to certifications tests which have to be passed before the pilot property activation.

Please reach our to our integration department ([integrations@clock-hs.com](https://mailto:integrations@clock-hs.com)) to schedule the integration tests.

The integration tests have approximate duration of 3 hours. The configured connection for your sandbox account will be used for testing the below scenarios\*:

1. **Availability and Rates push:  
    1.1. Full availability and prices push;  
    1.2. Availability change for selected dates;  
    1.3. Price change for selected dates;  
    1.4. LOS restrictions. Setting MinLOS and MaxLOS for selected days;  
    1.5. STOP restrictions. Setting Closed, Closed for Arrival, Closed for Departure for selected days;**

2. **Reservations retrieve:  
    2.1. Room reservation;  
    2.2. Multiple rooms reservation. All bookings should have the same reference number(ResID_Value) in order to appear as connected in ClockPMS+;  
    2.3. Multiple rates / prices per day reservation;  
    2.4. Booking with supplements;2.5. Booking update;  
    2.6. Booking cancellation;  
    2.7. Credit card data import. PLEASE NOTE: Credit Card should be send with the booking update only if changed!  
    2.8. Company mapping  
    2.9. Guest data transmission - Main guest/Contact person and Number of Adults/Children**

3. **Error handling:  
    3.1. Wrong room type code mapping;  
    3.2. Wrong rate code mapping;**


_\` \*'The scenarios may vary based on the features supported by the integration._
